WEBVTT

01:37.870 --> 01:40.990
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.100 --> 01:43.970
[Episode 26]

01:46.060 --> 01:50.380
[Xu Miyu]

01:54.560 --> 01:56.160
If you insist on thanking me,

01:57.509 --> 01:58.259
how about

01:59.509 --> 02:00.910
we have dinner together?

02:12.770 --> 02:15.090
[Tonight]

02:25.020 --> 02:26.880
Do you have any plans for tonight?

02:26.950 --> 02:27.770
Come with me

02:27.800 --> 02:28.820
to visit a restaurant.

02:28.820 --> 02:31.150
It sounds like
you're forcing her to work overtime.

02:31.150 --> 02:32.240
You evil boss.

02:34.000 --> 02:35.340
You scared me.

02:35.960 --> 02:37.680
I also want to fully support your

02:37.680 --> 02:39.280
hard-won spring.

02:39.590 --> 02:40.280
However,

02:40.810 --> 02:42.480
the winter of KPIs

02:42.500 --> 02:43.740
is coming soon.

02:46.030 --> 02:47.820
The Golden Week has just ended,

02:48.030 --> 02:51.020
and there are still two months
before the summer vacation begins.

02:48.079 --> 02:48.700
[Monthly Performance Report
of Purong Hotel]

02:49.520 --> 02:51.950
[Monthly Performance Report
of Purong Hotel]

02:51.910 --> 02:53.970
The rainy season is coming soon.

02:54.190 --> 02:55.560
The following days

02:56.420 --> 02:57.230
will be tough.

02:58.660 --> 02:58.980
[Monthly Performance Report
of Purong Hotel]

02:59.060 --> 03:01.410
[Statement of Expenditures]

03:01.410 --> 03:02.050
[Monthly Performance Report
of Purong Hotel]

03:10.000 --> 03:10.800
Come on.

03:11.120 --> 03:11.750
Back then,

03:11.750 --> 03:13.560
we took a fancy to this building
at first sight.

03:13.560 --> 03:15.510
It's the best one
in the entire residential compound.

03:15.510 --> 03:16.360
It really is.

03:16.680 --> 03:17.500
Look.

03:17.750 --> 03:19.550
The sunlight is great.

03:20.030 --> 03:20.560
As for the layout,

03:20.560 --> 03:23.360
it has great ventilation
from north to south, too.

03:23.610 --> 03:25.070
In summer,
when we open the window just a bit,

03:25.070 --> 03:26.200
there will be a breeze

03:26.200 --> 03:27.860
in the apartment constantly.

03:28.680 --> 03:30.000
The decoration style of your home

03:30.000 --> 03:31.190
is so classy.

03:31.190 --> 03:32.840
This TV feature wall

03:32.840 --> 03:34.030
looks so grand.

03:34.030 --> 03:34.560
Yes.

03:34.560 --> 03:36.030
What material is it made of?

03:36.030 --> 03:38.560
Fish Belly White Marble
imported from Italy.

03:38.590 --> 03:39.570
So beautiful!

03:41.280 --> 03:42.329
Come and take a look.

03:42.329 --> 03:43.050
Come on.

03:43.190 --> 03:44.050
Come over here.

03:46.400 --> 03:47.840
They specifically hired someone

03:47.840 --> 03:49.170
to design this nursery.

03:49.170 --> 03:50.930
You guys are so thoughtful.

03:52.280 --> 03:53.970
The baby isn't even born yet,

03:54.120 --> 03:55.170
but this whole room

03:55.170 --> 03:56.770
is already fully furnished.

03:57.840 --> 03:58.910
As for this crib,

03:59.120 --> 04:01.560
this brand is very expensive.

04:01.560 --> 04:02.800
Sure.

04:02.840 --> 04:04.970
It must cost tens of thousands of yuan.

04:05.840 --> 04:06.800
My son and daughter-in-law

04:06.800 --> 04:08.500
are both good at making money.

04:08.960 --> 04:11.080
Not only are they willing to spend money
for my grandson,

04:11.080 --> 04:12.080
but recently, they've also bought me

04:12.080 --> 04:13.590
a new pair of presbyopic glasses.

04:13.590 --> 04:14.710
Touch and feel them.

04:14.710 --> 04:15.240
They're very light.

04:15.240 --> 04:15.560
Yeah.

04:15.560 --> 04:16.810
So light.

04:17.430 --> 04:19.390
When you wear them,
it feels like you're not wearing them.

04:19.390 --> 04:20.810
They must be expensive.

04:21.269 --> 04:22.500
They just cost 18,000 yuan.

04:22.500 --> 04:23.830
Mom, the price isn't 18,000 yuan.

04:23.830 --> 04:24.830
It's 12,000 yuan.

04:25.560 --> 04:26.360
That's right.

04:26.720 --> 04:28.050
I have such a bad memory.

04:28.830 --> 04:30.720
You're becoming such a humblebragger.

04:30.720 --> 04:32.430
Just enjoy your happy life
with your son and grandchild.

04:32.430 --> 04:33.270
Right.

04:33.680 --> 04:36.270
We won't just enjoy the benefits
without helping them.

04:36.270 --> 04:37.870
Since the children treat us so well,

04:37.870 --> 04:38.870
as parents,

04:38.870 --> 04:40.680
we should also
show our appreciation, right?

04:40.680 --> 04:41.720
That's right.

04:41.720 --> 04:42.920
My husband and I

04:42.920 --> 04:44.210
have already discussed this.

04:44.210 --> 04:45.510
We'll pay for our daughter-in-law's

04:45.510 --> 04:46.510
postpartum care.

04:47.190 --> 04:48.520
You are such a role model

04:49.159 --> 04:50.270
as a mother-in-law.

04:50.270 --> 04:51.760
It's my duty.

04:52.000 --> 04:53.380
It's time to eat!

04:53.800 --> 04:54.360
Hurry up!

04:54.390 --> 04:55.480
Let's eat.

04:55.510 --> 04:56.690
It's time to eat.

04:59.630 --> 05:01.030
There are so many dishes.

05:01.680 --> 05:03.080
Make yourselves at home.

05:03.510 --> 05:04.560
What a good wife and loving mother.

05:04.560 --> 05:06.690
I wonder if it suits your taste.

05:09.000 --> 05:10.560
Your daughter-in-law is so capable.

05:10.560 --> 05:11.490
It's great.

05:11.980 --> 05:12.680
Stop working.

05:12.680 --> 05:13.380
Let's eat.

05:13.430 --> 05:14.460
The last dish.

05:15.430 --> 05:16.160
Remain seated.

05:16.160 --> 05:17.070
I'll go help her.

05:17.070 --> 05:18.370
Okay. Go ahead.

05:25.000 --> 05:25.660
You guys...

05:26.120 --> 05:27.920
You guys ordered takeout again?

05:28.500 --> 05:30.120
You should have told me earlier.

05:30.120 --> 05:32.880
I could have come
and prepared the meal for you in advance.

05:32.880 --> 05:33.610
Mom,

05:34.000 --> 05:35.120
you're out of date.

05:36.000 --> 05:37.720
This restaurant is very popular.

05:37.720 --> 05:38.970
It's authentic French cuisine.

05:38.970 --> 05:40.490
The most important thing is that

05:40.490 --> 05:41.320
she was

05:41.340 --> 05:42.700
afraid that the delivery guy

05:42.700 --> 05:43.870
would delay it,

05:44.200 --> 05:45.220
so even during pregnancy,

05:45.220 --> 05:46.370
she still went to the restaurant
to fetch the food.

05:46.370 --> 05:47.680
Don't you think that was so terrifying?

05:47.680 --> 05:48.940
You have to be careful.

05:49.890 --> 05:51.220
Why are you saying this?

05:51.940 --> 05:52.670
Mom.

05:52.700 --> 05:53.990
When I'm done with this busy period,

05:53.990 --> 05:55.630
I'll personally make some fresh meals

05:55.630 --> 05:56.840
for Yucheng.

05:57.330 --> 05:57.980
Okay.

06:24.140 --> 06:25.430
[Summons from the People's Court
of Hongkou District, Shanghai]

06:25.530 --> 06:27.310
What's there to see?

06:27.360 --> 06:28.390
What happened to you?

06:28.390 --> 06:30.120
Why did you get the court summons?

06:30.120 --> 06:31.240
What happened in the company before

06:31.240 --> 06:31.800
has been solved.

06:31.800 --> 06:33.240
It has nothing to do with me.

06:33.240 --> 06:34.040
Come back.

06:34.040 --> 06:35.900
I haven't finished speaking yet.

06:36.040 --> 06:36.600
Well...

06:37.920 --> 06:39.800
I noticed you didn't eat much today.

06:39.800 --> 06:40.600
Are you hungry?

06:40.600 --> 06:42.480
I'm not hungry. I have no appetite.

06:42.480 --> 06:44.040
Do you think I'm annoying now?

06:44.040 --> 06:45.159
No, I don't.

06:45.790 --> 06:47.480
Are you not feeling well?

06:47.480 --> 06:49.920
How about going to the hospital
to see the doctor?

06:49.920 --> 06:51.970
None of the questions you asked
was to the point.

06:51.970 --> 06:53.110
Are you doing this on purpose?

06:53.110 --> 06:53.550
I...

06:53.600 --> 06:54.800
How am I doing this on purpose?

06:54.800 --> 06:57.000
You know I've been under a lot of
pressure lately due to my company's KPIs,

06:57.000 --> 06:58.460
but you just won't help me.

06:58.830 --> 06:59.830
The company's team building activity

06:59.830 --> 07:01.390
isn't up to me alone,

07:01.390 --> 07:01.920
is it?

07:01.920 --> 07:03.060
You always have excuses.

07:03.060 --> 07:03.680
I just don't know

07:03.680 --> 07:05.160
what the use of your position

07:05.160 --> 07:06.410
as a vice president is,

07:06.410 --> 07:08.160
and what the use of marrying you is.

07:08.160 --> 07:10.020
Let's not make a big deal out of it.

07:10.830 --> 07:11.390
Alright.

07:11.480 --> 07:13.040
I'll discuss it. Okay?

07:13.040 --> 07:13.680
Not okay.

07:13.680 --> 07:14.920
Not a single word you said is sincere.

07:14.920 --> 07:16.580
You might as well say nothing.

07:23.390 --> 07:24.000
Fine.

07:24.240 --> 07:25.360
I promise you.

07:25.600 --> 07:26.360
About what?

07:26.600 --> 07:28.040
About the team building contract.

07:28.040 --> 07:29.600
What will you do
with the team building contract?

07:29.600 --> 07:31.270
I'll let you
get the team building contract,

07:31.270 --> 07:33.159
and it'll be held in Purong Hotel. Okay?

07:33.159 --> 07:34.800
That's more like it.

07:35.360 --> 07:36.720
You're happy now.

07:37.560 --> 07:39.090
I feel like he's kicking me.

07:39.120 --> 07:39.650
Alright.

07:39.800 --> 07:40.600
Get some rest.

07:40.920 --> 07:42.520
I'll go throw the trash away.

07:47.440 --> 07:49.000
The door is unlocked.

07:55.350 --> 07:56.600
The door is locked.

08:05.340 --> 08:06.230
[Summons from the People's Court
of Hongkou District, Shanghai]

08:06.250 --> 08:07.490
[Case Cause: Marital Property Dispute]

08:07.520 --> 08:09.040
[Summoned Party: Nie Yucheng]

08:27.630 --> 08:33.620
[Changyang Travel Company
—Corporate Team-Building]

08:27.940 --> 08:28.800
Be careful.

08:28.870 --> 08:29.530
Be careful.

08:29.920 --> 08:30.920
Lift it up a bit.

08:32.720 --> 08:33.860
Okay. Alright.

08:33.940 --> 08:35.000
Move it a bit to the right.

08:35.000 --> 08:38.770
[Changyang Travel Company
—Corporate Team-Building]

08:35.549 --> 08:36.750
Alright. Put it down.

08:37.909 --> 08:38.710
It's okay now.

08:38.720 --> 08:39.720
-Thank you, Mr. Ji.
-Thank you.

08:39.720 --> 08:40.650
You're welcome.

08:40.840 --> 08:41.720
Mr. Ji.

08:44.940 --> 08:48.070
[Changyang Travel Company
—Corporate Team-Building]

08:53.330 --> 08:55.950
[Changyang Travel Company
—Corporate Team-Building]

08:59.490 --> 09:00.890
Do you need to avoid them?

09:01.960 --> 09:02.650
No need.

09:03.030 --> 09:04.830
I can handle the reception work.

09:06.720 --> 09:07.240
Okay.

09:07.790 --> 09:09.450
I'm right by your side anyway.

09:12.030 --> 09:12.630
Thank you.

09:23.440 --> 09:24.450
Okay. Thank you.

09:24.630 --> 09:25.460
Mr. Nie.

09:26.180 --> 09:27.110
Nice to meet you.

09:27.550 --> 09:29.140
I'm Xue Rui,
assistant to the general manager.

09:29.140 --> 09:30.510
Hello, Mr. Xue.

09:30.730 --> 09:31.450
Where is Mr. Ji?

09:31.450 --> 09:33.850
He's waiting for you
at the entrance of the banquet hall.

09:33.850 --> 09:34.540
Honey!

09:36.600 --> 09:37.480
Mr. Xue.

09:37.480 --> 09:38.820
I'll take my husband upstairs now.

09:38.820 --> 09:39.240
Okay.

09:39.360 --> 09:40.790
Mr. Nie, this way please.

09:41.710 --> 09:42.840
I'm going upstairs.

09:45.010 --> 09:46.610
Give me your bag.

09:47.720 --> 09:49.120
They're going upstairs.

09:56.500 --> 09:57.550
Mr. Ji.

09:58.390 --> 09:58.910
Mr. Nie.

09:58.930 --> 10:00.240
-How have you been?
-How have you been?

10:00.240 --> 10:01.150
Thank you for coming.

10:01.150 --> 10:02.150
Don't mention it.

10:02.150 --> 10:03.270
You don't need to thank me.

10:03.270 --> 10:04.720
You should be thanking her.

10:04.720 --> 10:05.600
For this deal,

10:05.600 --> 10:07.240
she badgered me every day.

10:07.240 --> 10:09.050
She kept badgering me
even during pregnancy.

10:09.050 --> 10:10.360
This is my duty, isn't it?

10:10.360 --> 10:10.840
Yes.

10:10.840 --> 10:12.840
I just want to create profits
for the hotel.

10:12.840 --> 10:14.320
That has always been
what I've been striving for.

10:14.320 --> 10:15.360
Yes, yes, yes.

10:15.750 --> 10:16.720
Come on. Let's go inside and talk.

10:16.720 --> 10:17.120
Okay.

10:17.180 --> 10:17.870
Ms. Xu,

10:18.120 --> 10:19.520
please show them the way.

10:24.400 --> 10:25.400
Mr. Nie.

10:25.420 --> 10:26.450
Ms. Lu.

10:26.470 --> 10:27.500
If you need anything,

10:27.500 --> 10:28.280
just let me know anytime.

10:28.280 --> 10:28.890
Okay.

10:29.510 --> 10:30.510
Please follow me.

10:35.510 --> 10:36.120
Let's go.

10:44.200 --> 10:44.750
Please.

11:06.220 --> 11:07.360
Mr. and Mrs. Nie,

11:07.360 --> 11:08.490
here are your seats.

11:11.280 --> 11:12.040
Thank you.

11:12.410 --> 11:14.070
What are you thanking her for?

11:14.600 --> 11:16.460
Bring us some chrysanthemum tea.

11:17.240 --> 11:18.000
Ziyu.

11:19.650 --> 11:21.710
Mr. and Mrs. Nie
would like some chrysanthemum tea.

11:21.710 --> 11:22.560
Okay.

11:24.090 --> 11:25.360
If you two need anything else,

11:25.360 --> 11:26.290
just let me know.

11:26.320 --> 11:28.730
-Also bring me a cup of warm water.
-Ms. Lu, are you in the banquet hall?

11:28.730 --> 11:29.480
Yes, I am.

11:29.480 --> 11:31.100
Just leave the banquet hall to me.

11:31.100 --> 11:31.840
Ms. Lu,

11:31.840 --> 11:34.240
please reconfirm this guest list.

11:41.750 --> 11:42.480
Miyu.

11:42.480 --> 11:43.360
There's an emergency in the kitchen.

11:43.360 --> 11:45.090
They need you there right away.

11:46.720 --> 11:47.870
Ask the receptionists to check

11:47.870 --> 11:48.600
this list of yours carefully.

11:48.600 --> 11:49.840
There are definitely some mistakes.

11:49.840 --> 11:50.320
Okay.

11:55.360 --> 11:55.870
Mr. Gu.

11:55.870 --> 11:56.360
Hello, Mr. Gu.

11:56.360 --> 11:57.270
Mr. Gu is here.

11:57.300 --> 11:58.560
Let's go greet him now.

11:59.690 --> 12:00.520
Mr. Gu.

12:01.240 --> 12:02.000
Welcome.

12:02.000 --> 12:02.480
Hello.

12:02.560 --> 12:03.990
Come on. This way, please.

12:03.990 --> 12:04.550
Come on.

12:05.000 --> 12:06.600
Hello, Mr. Gu.

12:06.600 --> 12:08.110
You're finally here.

12:08.110 --> 12:10.000
I even saw Mrs. Gu yesterday.

12:11.200 --> 12:12.080
Come on. Please have a seat.

12:12.080 --> 12:12.740
Have a seat.

12:27.600 --> 12:28.510
Mom.

12:29.940 --> 12:32.000
Why are you throwing a tantrum again?

12:32.840 --> 12:34.600
Didn't we agree on this yesterday?

12:34.600 --> 12:35.950
There's no performance
at the Jazz Bar tonight.

12:35.950 --> 12:37.090
It has been switched to the day shift.

12:37.090 --> 12:38.720
There are 300 people upstairs
having a team building activity.

12:38.720 --> 12:39.840
If they all eat your boat pastries,

12:39.840 --> 12:41.120
won't that be great advertising for you?

12:41.120 --> 12:43.250
I'll make pastries for anyone but her.

12:46.400 --> 12:48.280
Mom, who are you upset with now?

12:48.310 --> 12:50.130
It's all because of that Lu Zhenzhen.

12:50.130 --> 12:50.720
No wonder

12:50.720 --> 12:53.290
she came to the restaurant
bossing people around early in the morning.

12:53.290 --> 12:55.620
It turns out
she's in charge of this order.

12:55.780 --> 12:58.180
I'm not taking the order
she's in charge of.

13:08.520 --> 13:10.920
What are you doing?
Are you driving me away?

13:12.440 --> 13:13.050
Mom.

13:13.600 --> 13:15.000
Lu Zhenzhen has been Purong Hotel's

13:15.000 --> 13:17.000
monthly sales champion
for six consecutive months.

13:17.000 --> 13:18.090
Some of her clients

13:18.240 --> 13:19.720
would stay at the hotel,

13:19.870 --> 13:21.630
some would get gym memberships
at the Health Club,

13:21.630 --> 13:22.840
some would get massages here
all year round,

13:22.840 --> 13:24.300
and some would often come here to eat.

13:24.300 --> 13:25.720
They are all over our entire hotel.

13:25.720 --> 13:27.300
If you can't accept it,

13:27.330 --> 13:28.590
you might as well quit.

13:30.010 --> 13:31.720
I'm just losing my temper, aren't I?

13:31.720 --> 13:32.720
Gosh.

13:32.960 --> 13:35.950
You have no idea
how much I can't stand seeing her face.

13:35.950 --> 13:37.150
When I think about

13:37.170 --> 13:39.830
letting her eat such delicious pastries,

13:40.200 --> 13:42.270
how I wish I could mix some sand in them.

13:42.270 --> 13:42.910
Mom.

13:43.260 --> 13:45.630
Please don't talk nonsense
outside like this, okay?

13:45.630 --> 13:47.200
If you don't
take your own specialty seriously,

13:47.200 --> 13:48.350
you might as well quit.

13:48.350 --> 13:50.680
You're just ruining your own reputation.

13:51.510 --> 13:53.360
I'm just losing my temper, aren't I?

13:53.360 --> 13:54.360
Gosh.

13:54.420 --> 13:56.180
When I make the pastries later,

13:56.470 --> 13:57.520
I'll close my eyes.

13:57.520 --> 13:58.360
I won't look at

13:58.360 --> 13:59.600
or listen to anything.

13:59.600 --> 14:00.600
Is that okay?

14:01.230 --> 14:02.360
That's more like it.

14:02.880 --> 14:04.950
Then later, just stay in the kitchen
and make pastries.

14:04.950 --> 14:06.460
Don't go anywhere. Okay?

14:07.380 --> 14:08.870
Okay?

14:10.060 --> 14:11.300
Okay.

14:13.570 --> 14:14.290
It's a deal.

14:28.700 --> 14:29.500
Isn't this...

14:30.530 --> 14:31.410
Miyu?

14:31.480 --> 14:32.360
Hello, Mr. Hu.

14:32.900 --> 14:34.260
You're incredible.

14:34.360 --> 14:36.240
Others get one year older every year,

14:36.240 --> 14:38.000
but you're getting younger

14:38.000 --> 14:40.080
and prettier.

14:40.080 --> 14:41.910
Happy events bring good spirits.

14:41.910 --> 14:43.480
Changyang is holding
such an important team-building event

14:43.480 --> 14:44.870
in our hotel,

14:44.870 --> 14:46.240
which is the highest recognition of

14:46.240 --> 14:47.840
the service quality of our hotel.

14:47.840 --> 14:50.000
Of course I will present my best demeanor

14:50.000 --> 14:51.660
to welcome all my old friends.

14:51.720 --> 14:53.180
Come on. This way, please.

14:54.080 --> 14:55.080
Mr. Hu.

14:55.480 --> 14:56.870
I'm here to welcome you personally.

14:56.870 --> 14:57.840
Mrs. Nie.

14:57.920 --> 14:59.000
-Please come in.
-Okay.

14:59.000 --> 14:59.510
Please.

15:03.630 --> 15:04.840
Here, Mr. Hu.

15:06.120 --> 15:07.360
-Mr. Hu.
-Mr. Hu.

15:07.480 --> 15:08.870
This way.

15:09.200 --> 15:09.960
Mr. Hu.

15:10.340 --> 15:11.100
Nie.

15:12.120 --> 15:13.520
You did a good job on this event.

15:13.520 --> 15:14.610
I'm flattered.

15:14.640 --> 15:15.490
Keep up the good work.

15:15.490 --> 15:16.360
Got it.

15:17.080 --> 15:19.240
Why is there one set of tableware missing?
Waiter!

15:19.240 --> 15:20.770
Come on. Please have a seat.

15:26.000 --> 15:26.720
Miyu.

15:26.740 --> 15:27.680
Mr. Hu.

15:28.360 --> 15:29.750
My wife

15:29.750 --> 15:32.620
keeps talking about
your spiced beef every day.

15:33.000 --> 15:34.410
As for her precious son,

15:34.600 --> 15:36.480
if he doesn't
have your spiced beef for a day,

15:36.480 --> 15:37.600
he just can't eat his meals properly.

15:37.600 --> 15:39.100
It's very kind of you to say that.

15:39.100 --> 15:41.120
Actually, our Chinese restaurant has many

15:41.120 --> 15:42.240
delicious dishes.

15:42.270 --> 15:44.120
If you have the chance,
you can bring your wife

15:44.120 --> 15:46.250
and child here to taste them together.

15:46.360 --> 15:47.000
Sure.

15:47.750 --> 15:50.210
I'll bring them here to dine
when I have time.

15:50.500 --> 15:51.410
Please enjoy your meal first.

15:51.410 --> 15:53.210
Let me know if you need anything.

15:58.810 --> 15:59.630
Nie.

16:01.120 --> 16:02.120
Did you see that?

16:02.520 --> 16:04.180
It's only been a few months
since you two broke up.

16:04.180 --> 16:06.140
Just see how much she has changed.

16:06.960 --> 16:09.360
It's obvious
she has a bright future ahead.

16:10.360 --> 16:11.510
When I walked up to her just now,

16:11.510 --> 16:12.510
I was really surprised.

16:12.510 --> 16:13.360
Mrs. Nie... No, no.

16:13.360 --> 16:15.000
I mean, Miyu.

16:15.120 --> 16:16.220
She has changed so much.

16:16.220 --> 16:17.120
You didn't see this just now.

16:17.120 --> 16:18.870
When she gave instructions to the waiters,

16:18.870 --> 16:20.750
she was so sharp-eyed and quick-witted.

16:20.750 --> 16:22.840
She has the exact vibe
of a workplace elite.

16:22.840 --> 16:26.720
Then it looks like getting divorced
isn't a bad thing after all.

16:28.840 --> 16:29.730
Zhenzhen.

16:29.840 --> 16:30.720
Are you speaking ill of me?

16:30.720 --> 16:32.110
-No.
-No.

16:32.470 --> 16:34.480
Today is your team-building day,

16:34.480 --> 16:36.200
and this is my home turf, too.

16:36.200 --> 16:37.630
We need to support each other.

16:37.630 --> 16:39.000
Absolutely, Zhenzhen.

16:38.940 --> 16:42.000
[Homecoming, Courteous Reception]

16:39.630 --> 16:40.240
Alright.

16:49.320 --> 16:50.510
Okay. I got it.

16:51.510 --> 16:53.110
Can I talk to you for a moment?

16:53.720 --> 16:54.280
Mr. Nie.

16:54.480 --> 16:56.540
I'm sorry but I'm very busy right now.

17:00.090 --> 17:01.690
Let's just talk for a moment.

17:04.720 --> 17:06.579
I've received the court summons.

17:06.920 --> 17:08.910
Is there any misunderstanding between us?

17:08.910 --> 17:10.310
We agreed on it when we got divorced.

17:10.310 --> 17:11.380
Why did you really sue me?

17:11.380 --> 17:13.400
You concealed the marital property first.

17:13.400 --> 17:15.160
I just took legal measures.

17:15.190 --> 17:16.670
You've misunderstood me.

17:16.790 --> 17:19.230
Honestly speaking,
I've given you everything that I could.

17:19.230 --> 17:20.720
That investment fund is already gone.

17:20.720 --> 17:22.069
You know that clearly.

17:22.069 --> 17:25.069
Then where did you get the money
to buy a new apartment?

17:28.000 --> 17:29.020
How did you find out about that?

17:29.020 --> 17:30.350
Did you investigate me?

17:31.480 --> 17:32.240
If you don't want anyone to know,

17:32.240 --> 17:33.970
just don't do it from the start.

17:34.310 --> 17:36.640
Miyu, I don't think this is necessary
since we were once married.

17:36.640 --> 17:38.200
Going to court would be embarrassing.

17:38.200 --> 17:39.590
If you are short of money, just tell me.

17:39.590 --> 17:43.000
-I'll give you money.
-I just want to claim what is rightfully mine.

17:43.000 --> 17:43.920
You weren't like this before.

17:43.920 --> 17:45.200
What was I like before?

17:45.970 --> 17:46.700
Nie Yucheng.

17:47.030 --> 17:48.240
If you think I'm still that Xu Miyu

17:48.240 --> 17:49.830
who can be bullied so easily,

17:49.830 --> 17:51.240
I have nothing to say to you.

17:51.240 --> 17:52.240
See you in court.

17:52.240 --> 17:53.720
Well, I...

17:53.720 --> 17:55.850
What do you mean by seeing him in court?

17:58.590 --> 17:59.990
Don't talk about it here.

18:00.200 --> 18:01.190
Xu Miyu.

18:01.750 --> 18:02.980
Have you no shame at all?

18:02.980 --> 18:04.000
You've been divorced for so long,

18:04.000 --> 18:05.480
and you're still asking your ex-husband
for money?

18:05.480 --> 18:07.560
This is something
between Nie Yucheng and me.

18:07.560 --> 18:09.090
It's none of your business.

18:09.820 --> 18:10.680
Let go!

18:10.700 --> 18:11.700
I'm his wife.

18:14.240 --> 18:15.170
Xu Miyu.

18:15.200 --> 18:16.480
I'm warning you.

18:16.500 --> 18:18.740
If you dare to take this to court,

18:18.770 --> 18:21.830
I'll make sure
you can't make a living in this industry.

18:24.350 --> 18:25.240
You bad woman!

18:25.480 --> 18:28.070
-Don't you dare touch my daughter!
-Mom, why are you here?

18:28.070 --> 18:29.510
Don't you dare give it a try!

18:29.510 --> 18:30.480
You wretched hag.

18:30.480 --> 18:32.830
-Can you educate your daughter properly?
-What are you talking about?

18:32.830 --> 18:34.350
She's always acting like a beggar,

18:34.350 --> 18:35.000
asking for money everywhere.

18:35.000 --> 18:35.640
Bah!

18:35.640 --> 18:37.070
My daughter is asking for her own money.

18:37.070 --> 18:38.110
What does it have to do with you?

18:38.110 --> 18:38.830
Nie Yucheng!

18:38.830 --> 18:40.830
If you have any shame, don't play tricks.

18:40.830 --> 18:42.880
Just pay off your massive debt!

18:42.880 --> 18:44.960
Otherwise,
regarding your cheating scandals,

18:44.960 --> 18:47.000
I'll shout about them so loud
that the whole world will know.

18:47.000 --> 18:47.750
-Mom,
-Believe it or not.

18:47.750 --> 18:48.880
Just shout then.

18:48.880 --> 18:50.380
You'd better shout louder.

18:50.380 --> 18:51.960
Otherwise, I'll tell the police

18:51.960 --> 18:53.400
how you and your husband

18:53.400 --> 18:56.440
extorted my husband.

18:56.440 --> 18:57.640
Let's see who will suffer more.

18:57.640 --> 18:58.960
-Just tell the police then!
-Mom!

18:58.960 --> 19:00.480
Don't touch her.

19:00.480 --> 19:01.960
Just tell the police if you dare!

19:01.960 --> 19:02.720
Believe it or not...

19:02.720 --> 19:03.720
Tell the police if you dare!

19:03.720 --> 19:04.920
Just tell the police!

19:05.310 --> 19:06.440
Why did you hit her, Mom?

19:06.440 --> 19:07.510
I'm not your mom!

19:09.000 --> 19:10.440
You call her Mom?

19:26.720 --> 19:27.520
Here, Mr. Nie.

19:28.480 --> 19:29.160
Mr. Ji.

19:29.680 --> 19:31.070
After all, Zhenzhen is pregnant.

19:31.070 --> 19:32.880
Doing this is certainly inappropriate.

19:32.880 --> 19:34.310
-That's right.
-So I think whether...

19:34.310 --> 19:35.510
you can give us an explanation.

19:35.510 --> 19:35.720
Yes.

19:35.720 --> 19:38.440
You were the ones
who upset my daughter first.

19:38.440 --> 19:40.470
What kind of explanation do you want?

19:40.470 --> 19:43.070
Mr. and Mrs. Nie,
you've been treated unfairly.

19:43.070 --> 19:43.830
This matter

19:43.860 --> 19:45.860
is indeed my management failure

19:46.160 --> 19:47.510
as the general manager.

19:48.270 --> 19:51.130
Please allow me
to sincerely apologize to you both.

19:56.870 --> 19:58.200
Mr. Nie, how about this?

19:58.240 --> 20:00.220
I'll arrange for Mrs. Nie
to go to the hospital

20:00.220 --> 20:01.270
for a checkup as soon as possible.

20:01.270 --> 20:02.730
All the expenses incurred

20:02.740 --> 20:04.500
will be covered by our hotel.

20:06.960 --> 20:07.550
Mr. Ji.

20:08.030 --> 20:08.510
Shouldn't these expenses

20:08.510 --> 20:10.310
be covered by the two of them?

20:10.720 --> 20:12.180
We can cover the expenses.

20:13.000 --> 20:15.220
Ms. Xu is an employee of our hotel,

20:15.310 --> 20:17.620
and Chef Jiao is a cooperation consultant
of our hotel.

20:17.620 --> 20:20.480
Their matters should be
the responsibility of our hotel.

20:20.480 --> 20:21.480
And we'll definitely do our best

20:21.480 --> 20:23.550
to compensate you for your losses.

20:23.790 --> 20:24.720
But Ms. Lu,

20:25.290 --> 20:26.640
you are also an employee of our hotel.

20:26.640 --> 20:28.640
You should know that this is a hotel,

20:29.130 --> 20:31.330
not a place to settle personal grudges.

20:32.000 --> 20:33.400
So, please also respect

20:33.400 --> 20:35.030
our hotel's principles
of handling matters.

20:35.030 --> 20:35.680
Mr. Ji.

20:35.950 --> 20:38.010
I don't care about personal grudges.

20:38.200 --> 20:39.070
I am worried about the safety

20:39.070 --> 20:40.480
of the baby in my belly.

20:41.270 --> 20:43.800
You can't treat me
so unfairly like this, huh?

20:48.880 --> 20:50.030
Mr. Ji, do you think this...

20:50.030 --> 20:51.360
That's why I've told you

20:51.480 --> 20:53.550
to go to the hospital for a checkup
as soon as possible.

20:53.550 --> 20:55.480
We will take full responsibility.

20:58.000 --> 20:58.640
Mr. Nie.

20:59.720 --> 21:00.720
We've

21:00.720 --> 21:02.980
always been good cooperative partners.

21:03.240 --> 21:05.550
You probably don't want this matter

21:05.550 --> 21:07.480
to affect our future cooperation, either.

21:07.480 --> 21:08.740
Please, for my sake...

21:09.240 --> 21:09.880
Let's...

21:11.480 --> 21:12.270
let this go.

21:22.200 --> 21:22.550
Okay.

21:32.240 --> 21:33.550
Mr. Ji, I'm sorry.

21:34.790 --> 21:36.670
My mother shouldn't have hit her.

21:37.030 --> 21:38.240
I failed to stop her,

21:39.480 --> 21:41.210
so it's my responsibility, too.

21:41.210 --> 21:42.890
If you must punish someone,
just punish me.

21:42.890 --> 21:43.950
I'll accept it all.

21:45.000 --> 21:48.060
It was indeed inappropriate
for your mother to hit her.

21:48.160 --> 21:49.510
But what I want to say is that

21:49.510 --> 21:50.770
you did nothing wrong,

21:51.270 --> 21:53.000
so you don't need to apologize.

21:57.480 --> 22:00.440
Today,
whether you're an employee or a guest,

22:01.480 --> 22:03.140
first of all, you are a person.

22:04.790 --> 22:07.390
Letting others know you're not someone
who can be easily bullied

22:07.390 --> 22:09.380
is a right you should have.

22:39.680 --> 22:41.000
The door is locked.

22:55.310 --> 22:57.240
Here. Change into these slippers.

23:08.270 --> 23:10.200
If I hadn't found out about it
early today,

23:10.200 --> 23:12.270
were you going to give her money
behind my back?

23:12.270 --> 23:14.800
You've got more money
than you can spend, huh?

23:14.960 --> 23:16.480
I was just afraid you would worry,

23:16.480 --> 23:17.240
so I wanted to try reasoning

23:17.240 --> 23:18.190
with her first.

23:18.440 --> 23:20.510
What's there to reason with her about?

23:20.510 --> 23:21.640
I won't allow you
to give our family's money

23:21.640 --> 23:22.480
to that woman.

23:22.720 --> 23:26.270
Find the best lawyer to defend yourself
against her charges in court.

23:26.270 --> 23:27.480
Why do you keep squatting there?

23:27.480 --> 23:28.370
Did you hear me?

23:28.400 --> 23:29.880
I heard you.

23:30.550 --> 23:31.480
My stomach hurts.

23:31.480 --> 23:32.680
Could you pour me a glass of hot water?

23:32.680 --> 23:33.680
Your stomach never hurt

23:33.680 --> 23:35.030
until I started talking about
serious matters.

23:35.030 --> 23:36.230
Just endure the pain.

24:25.030 --> 24:27.240
Though that little vixen was so arrogant,

24:27.240 --> 24:29.900
I still got to slap her face hard today,
didn't I?

24:30.640 --> 24:32.350
You saw how she looked today.

24:32.840 --> 24:33.790
It helped to vent my anger,

24:33.790 --> 24:35.190
and it was so gratifying.

24:39.480 --> 24:40.720
Tell me the truth.

24:42.000 --> 24:42.790
About what?

24:44.030 --> 24:45.090
You and Mr. Ji...

24:45.270 --> 24:46.590
Mom, here you go again.

24:46.620 --> 24:48.160
Just calm down.

24:48.160 --> 24:50.510
You always have this attitude
whenever I mention this matter.

24:50.510 --> 24:52.270
Because you always pair me off
with him arbitrarily.

24:52.270 --> 24:54.070
How am I doing that arbitrarily?

24:54.070 --> 24:55.310
Just think about what happened today.

24:55.310 --> 24:58.160
A general manager stood in front of you

24:58.160 --> 24:59.310
and apologized to that vixen

24:59.310 --> 25:01.060
so humbly.

25:01.270 --> 25:02.690
What did he mean?

25:02.790 --> 25:04.590
Even a blind person could see it.

25:06.400 --> 25:07.070
This matter

25:07.070 --> 25:09.240
is indeed my management failure

25:09.240 --> 25:10.680
as the general manager.

25:11.240 --> 25:14.160
Please allow me
to sincerely apologize to you both.

25:16.550 --> 25:17.440
In my opinion,

25:17.440 --> 25:18.240
isn't that little vixen

25:18.240 --> 25:20.640
just relying on the fact
that Nie Yucheng has a bit of ability?

25:20.640 --> 25:22.790
That's why she can show off
in front of you.

25:22.790 --> 25:25.720
She even dared to complain it
to the general manager.

25:26.480 --> 25:28.310
Who does she think she is to do that?

25:28.310 --> 25:29.970
If you and Mr. Ji are together,

25:30.920 --> 25:33.310
wouldn't you become her direct boss?

25:33.510 --> 25:34.480
By that time,

25:34.480 --> 25:37.140
even Nie will have to fawn on you.

25:37.170 --> 25:38.200
Let's see

25:38.220 --> 25:41.150
if they would still dare to act wildly
in front of you.

25:41.500 --> 25:42.780
But let me tell you.

25:42.920 --> 25:44.720
No matter what happens in the future,

25:44.720 --> 25:46.510
you can't be as impulsive as today.

25:46.510 --> 25:47.160
Okay?

25:47.270 --> 25:48.240
Look at you.

25:48.240 --> 25:49.500
What a little ingrate.

25:49.680 --> 25:51.880
I'm venting anger
and taking revenge for you.

25:51.880 --> 25:53.310
I'm just afraid you'll get hurt.

25:53.310 --> 25:54.310
Besides,

25:54.920 --> 25:56.560
isn't your daughter doing well now?

25:56.560 --> 25:58.240
Why do you always care so much about them?

25:58.240 --> 26:00.040
They bullied you so much before.

26:00.270 --> 26:01.750
Can you really forgive them?

26:01.750 --> 26:02.940
Let me give you an example.

26:02.940 --> 26:04.750
For instance,
when you're walking on the street,

26:04.750 --> 26:05.750
a piece of chewing gum

26:05.750 --> 26:07.510
accidentally gets stuck to your shoe.

26:07.510 --> 26:09.230
You definitely want to get rid of it,

26:09.230 --> 26:09.920
right?

26:09.920 --> 26:11.760
You just can't
fight with that chewing gum, right?

26:11.760 --> 26:12.400
Then...

26:12.920 --> 26:14.070
Then what if they do it again in the...

26:14.070 --> 26:16.470
If they dare to bully me again
in the future,

26:16.480 --> 26:18.270
I just won't stand there obediently

26:18.270 --> 26:19.930
to let them hit me like before.

26:20.350 --> 26:21.080
Don't worry.

26:37.780 --> 26:38.720
[High Output Management]

26:38.930 --> 26:40.440
You're reading a management book, huh?

26:40.440 --> 26:41.680
Mr. Tan.

26:43.550 --> 26:45.340
So you want to be a professional manager?

26:45.340 --> 26:47.270
I'm just setting a goal for myself.

26:47.400 --> 26:48.880
Am I being too unrealistic?

26:48.880 --> 26:50.750
No, it's good to have a dream.

26:50.750 --> 26:51.480
However,

26:52.400 --> 26:54.060
being a professional manager

26:54.310 --> 26:55.370
is such a tough job.

26:55.480 --> 26:56.880
Actually, you don't have to work so hard.

26:56.880 --> 26:58.000
No matter what you do,

26:58.000 --> 26:59.440
you are just the best in my mind.

26:59.440 --> 27:00.000
Really.

27:01.440 --> 27:02.530
Are you leaving tonight?

27:02.530 --> 27:03.160
Yes.

27:03.160 --> 27:04.160
The car will be here soon.

27:04.160 --> 27:04.850
Oh, right.

27:06.000 --> 27:06.750
Okay.

27:09.200 --> 27:10.030
Then let me see you out.

27:10.030 --> 27:10.640
Okay.

27:11.030 --> 27:12.030
I can do it myself.

27:18.750 --> 27:19.510
Thanks.

27:21.000 --> 27:21.850
Mr. Tan.

27:22.310 --> 27:23.640
I haven't had the chance to thank you

27:23.640 --> 27:25.240
for what happened last time.

27:27.150 --> 27:28.950
Thank you for helping me so much.

27:29.240 --> 27:31.750
And I was drunk last time.

27:31.750 --> 27:35.480
If I did something rude,

27:35.480 --> 27:36.480
please forgive me.

27:36.480 --> 27:37.160
No, no.

27:37.160 --> 27:39.570
Actually, I was thoughtless last time,

27:39.600 --> 27:41.510
which caused you trouble.

27:41.510 --> 27:42.400
Of course not.

27:42.400 --> 27:43.480
You helped me.

27:45.070 --> 27:47.150
I merely helped you out of a tight spot.

27:47.150 --> 27:48.680
If I really want to help you,

27:48.790 --> 27:50.920
I actually would like to take you away.

27:52.030 --> 27:52.510
Um,

27:52.530 --> 27:53.750
I mean,

27:54.270 --> 27:55.030
I-I know you

27:55.030 --> 27:56.160
really like your job here,

27:56.160 --> 27:57.790
but the environment is still too tough.

27:57.790 --> 27:59.000
My company is also hiring.

27:59.000 --> 28:00.260
Would you like to come?

28:04.400 --> 28:06.750
Where are you
flying to this time, Mr. Tan?

28:06.930 --> 28:07.610
Hong Kong.

28:08.350 --> 28:10.120
I've moved my business to Hong Kong

28:10.120 --> 28:12.210
so that I can come here often.

28:13.250 --> 28:14.920
If you live closer to the old Mr. Tan,

28:14.920 --> 28:15.920
it'll be convenient to take care of him.

28:15.920 --> 28:17.450
And I can also see you often.

28:21.310 --> 28:22.310
The car is here.

28:24.920 --> 28:25.880
Okay. Thanks.

28:29.970 --> 28:31.570
Take care. See you next time.

28:31.640 --> 28:32.640
See you next time.

28:43.840 --> 28:44.880
No wonder

28:45.720 --> 28:48.450
this girl doesn't
even like the general manager.

28:49.360 --> 28:51.090
So this is what's going on?

29:09.930 --> 29:11.340
Hello. This way.

29:11.920 --> 29:12.240
Come on.

29:12.240 --> 29:12.970
Give it to me.

29:16.790 --> 29:17.310
Here you are.

29:17.310 --> 29:18.390
Okay. Thank you.

29:18.420 --> 29:19.280
Please come in.

29:23.920 --> 29:26.120
This rainy season is so annoying.

30:03.390 --> 30:04.260
Honey.

30:05.160 --> 30:06.900
This rainy season is so annoying.

30:06.900 --> 30:09.210
My shoes got wet after a few steps.

30:17.370 --> 30:18.720
A few days ago,
I noticed that Bottega Veneta

30:18.720 --> 30:19.830
released a new pair of rain boots.

30:19.830 --> 30:20.750
They look pretty nice.

30:20.750 --> 30:21.750
I want to buy them.

30:27.630 --> 30:28.720
What are you busy with?

30:28.720 --> 30:31.320
Why aren't you
replying to my WeChat messages?

30:36.790 --> 30:37.720
It's damp.

30:37.720 --> 30:38.480
Bake it again.

30:38.480 --> 30:39.420
If it's still not okay,
just throw it away.

30:39.420 --> 30:39.950
Alright.

30:43.000 --> 30:43.640
Ya.

30:44.330 --> 30:46.050
Remind the warehouse that

30:46.080 --> 30:48.000
food easily gets moldy in this weather.

30:48.000 --> 30:49.480
Ask them
to make sure to check the ingredients.

30:49.480 --> 30:50.000
Okay.

31:08.880 --> 31:09.670
Hello, Mr. Ji.

31:09.670 --> 31:11.550
Here is the Red Bean and Coix Seed Water‌
you ordered.

31:11.550 --> 31:12.890
I'll hang a dehumidifier bag for you.

31:12.890 --> 31:13.440
Come in.

31:24.460 --> 31:25.460
Thank you.

31:31.940 --> 31:33.200
I think it tastes good.

31:33.400 --> 31:36.600
Ask Chef Li to add a little
dried tangerine peel to it, too.

31:37.030 --> 31:39.500
This sweet soup
can help to remove dampness.

31:39.530 --> 31:40.420
We can offer it as a free gift

31:40.420 --> 31:42.380
to the guests
who check in during the rainy season.

31:42.380 --> 31:43.640
I think your idea is great.

31:43.640 --> 31:44.700
I'll go arrange it now.

31:44.700 --> 31:45.190
Okay.

31:50.620 --> 31:53.890
[Purong Hotel
Performance Analysis Statistical Table]

31:53.990 --> 31:55.330
[The Purpose of the Activity]

32:06.080 --> 32:07.080
I'm sorry, Mr. Ji.

32:07.790 --> 32:08.750
Our chief editor said

32:08.750 --> 32:10.160
the rain in the suburbs was so heavy

32:10.160 --> 32:11.960
that he couldn't make it by noon.

32:12.670 --> 32:14.000
Then what about dinner?

32:14.160 --> 32:15.200
It's not very safe

32:15.720 --> 32:16.920
to travel at night.

32:16.920 --> 32:17.580
Besides,

32:18.160 --> 32:18.680
our chief editor

32:18.680 --> 32:22.200
has already checked into
the InterContinental Hotel over there.

32:22.200 --> 32:23.200
It's getting late.

32:23.200 --> 32:24.440
We should take our leave.

32:24.440 --> 32:24.880
Okay.

32:26.900 --> 32:27.720
Mr. Ji,

32:27.880 --> 32:29.480
the price we just mentioned

32:29.480 --> 32:31.690
is already the highest one we can offer.

32:31.720 --> 32:32.630
Mr. Ji, please

32:32.750 --> 32:33.950
think about it again.

32:34.000 --> 32:34.680
Okay.

32:34.720 --> 32:36.460
We will think about it seriously.

32:36.460 --> 32:37.030
Okay.

32:37.050 --> 32:37.910
I'll leave now.

32:38.750 --> 32:40.280
Okay. Let me see you all out.

32:45.240 --> 32:47.700
Should we
talk to their deputy editor again?

32:49.200 --> 32:50.400
What they originally wanted

32:50.400 --> 32:52.200
were two venues,
one indoor and one outdoor,

32:52.200 --> 32:53.480
which complemented each other.

32:53.480 --> 32:55.140
But now with the rainy season,

32:55.310 --> 32:57.070
the garden terrace cannot be used.

32:57.070 --> 32:58.720
It's not surprising
that they want a lower price.

32:58.720 --> 33:01.240
We've already offered them
the lowest price.

33:01.240 --> 33:02.640
If we accept the price they offered,

33:02.640 --> 33:04.770
we will definitely lose money on this.

33:09.180 --> 33:13.440
[Purong Hotel]

33:12.680 --> 33:13.240
Mr. Ji.

33:14.000 --> 33:15.000
You must have stayed

33:15.000 --> 33:16.930
in the deserts abroad for too long.

33:17.050 --> 33:18.000
Have you forgotten

33:18.000 --> 33:20.750
the most annoying thing
about Shanghai is this rainy season?

33:20.750 --> 33:21.510
Now look.

33:22.070 --> 33:22.920
Without a backup plan,

33:22.920 --> 33:24.720
our business is badly affected.

33:25.160 --> 33:25.880
Mr. Ji.

33:26.270 --> 33:26.790
Don't forget that

33:26.790 --> 33:29.390
we have a VAM agreement
hanging over our heads.

33:29.480 --> 33:31.140
What do you think we should do?

33:34.240 --> 33:36.240
Thank you for reminding me, Mr. Wei.

33:36.620 --> 33:38.080
I did stay in the desert regions

33:38.080 --> 33:39.270
of the Middle East and North Africa

33:39.270 --> 33:40.960
for a period of time.

33:41.550 --> 33:43.680
And I interacted a lot with the locals.

33:44.130 --> 33:45.060
Those residents

33:45.550 --> 33:47.640
in the tropical desert climate zone

33:47.640 --> 33:50.170
are very passionate
about watching the rain.

33:50.270 --> 33:51.200
Our off-season

33:51.200 --> 33:53.640
might just be their peak season.

33:55.590 --> 33:57.070
Did you all hear that?

33:57.640 --> 33:58.700
Watching the rain?

33:59.340 --> 34:00.900
Are you joking with us?

34:00.930 --> 34:01.810
Mr. Ji.

34:02.380 --> 34:03.440
Elaborate on that.

34:04.160 --> 34:04.920
Okay.

34:07.870 --> 34:09.070
[North Africa Rain Viewing Group Planning]

34:09.199 --> 34:10.280
Currently, we've established

34:10.280 --> 34:13.540
partnerships with eight travel agencies
in North Africa.

34:13.550 --> 34:15.230
This year, they will open up

34:15.230 --> 34:17.190
a new route
for watching rain in East Asia.

34:17.190 --> 34:19.449
From this week until the end of the month,

34:19.449 --> 34:20.320
these rain-viewing groups

34:20.320 --> 34:22.800
will check into
our Purong Hotel successively.

34:22.800 --> 34:24.550
That's just a drop in the bucket.

34:24.550 --> 34:26.800
Even if your so-called rain-viewing groups

34:26.800 --> 34:27.510
stay at our hotel,

34:27.510 --> 34:29.080
can they fill up all the guest rooms?

34:29.080 --> 34:30.800
And what should we do after they leave?

34:30.800 --> 34:34.510
Shall we find
cloud-viewing or star-viewing groups next?

34:34.610 --> 34:36.130
It's a temporary expedient indeed.

34:36.130 --> 34:37.040
But at least,

34:37.070 --> 34:39.400
it can increase the occupancy rate by 30%.

34:40.100 --> 34:41.710
Mr. Wei, do you have a way

34:41.730 --> 34:43.030
to solve this issue once and for all?

34:43.030 --> 34:45.480
You might as well bring it up
and discuss it with us all.

34:45.480 --> 34:45.960
I...

34:48.030 --> 34:48.710
Alright.

34:49.550 --> 34:51.880
Let's follow Mr. Ji's plan for now.

34:52.630 --> 34:53.230
Okay.

34:58.800 --> 35:00.190
-Welcome.
-Thank you.

35:01.000 --> 35:01.800
Welcome.

35:10.830 --> 35:14.010
Human joys and sorrows
are not mutually comprehensible.

35:14.010 --> 35:16.550
Some people would travel miles
to watch the rain,

35:16.550 --> 35:18.880
while some would get annoyed at the sight

35:18.880 --> 35:20.140
of this humid weather.

35:20.280 --> 35:22.740
Having business
is better than having none.

35:23.320 --> 35:26.070
The rain-viewing groups
can only help temporarily, not forever.

35:26.070 --> 35:27.070
Just wait and see.

35:27.480 --> 35:28.960
When this trend passes,

35:28.960 --> 35:30.960
we'll be back to the original state.

35:34.360 --> 35:35.110
Hello.

35:35.110 --> 35:36.770
Purong Hotel at your service.

35:38.840 --> 35:40.710
You'll check in on the night of June 6th

35:40.710 --> 35:42.800
and check out on the 10th. Is that right?

35:42.800 --> 35:44.530
A standard double room, right?

35:44.630 --> 35:45.920
Yes, we have standard double rooms.

35:45.920 --> 35:47.980
May I have your phone number, please?

35:48.190 --> 35:48.960
Ask the guest

35:48.960 --> 35:50.690
if he has any special requests.

35:51.370 --> 35:54.230
Do you have any specific requirements
for the room?

35:55.230 --> 35:56.820
You want a higher floor.

35:56.920 --> 35:58.400
You want it to be quiet.

36:00.480 --> 36:01.190
Don't worry.

36:01.190 --> 36:02.920
The soundproofing effect
in our hotel is excellent.

36:02.920 --> 36:04.400
Okay. We look forward to your visit.

36:04.400 --> 36:05.330
Goodbye, Ma'am.

36:07.400 --> 36:08.110
Lu Xiaoyan.

36:09.050 --> 36:10.230
Did you also receive bookings yesterday

36:10.230 --> 36:12.230
for June 6th to 9th?

36:13.880 --> 36:15.360
I think so.

36:15.360 --> 36:16.670
Check it right now.

36:18.510 --> 36:19.110
Okay.

36:20.800 --> 36:21.320
I found it.

36:21.320 --> 36:22.190
There is such a booking.

36:22.190 --> 36:23.280
The reservation is

36:23.280 --> 36:25.130
from the 6th to the 9th of next month.

36:25.130 --> 36:26.370
Please check again to see

36:26.370 --> 36:27.400
whether there are other bookings

36:27.400 --> 36:28.590
during this period.

36:28.670 --> 36:30.070
Why are we checking this?

36:30.840 --> 36:31.510
Yes.

36:34.180 --> 36:35.960
I found five bookings in total.

36:35.960 --> 36:38.070
Four of them are from the 6th to the 9th,

36:38.070 --> 36:40.880
and one is from the 6th to the 10th.

36:43.840 --> 36:46.320
We also need to
inform the colleagues on other shifts

36:46.320 --> 36:47.230
about this.

36:47.230 --> 36:49.510
Any bookings between the 6th and the 9th

36:49.510 --> 36:51.840
or the 10th of next month

36:51.840 --> 36:53.400
should be marked with notes.

36:53.400 --> 36:54.990
Then send the information
to Shi Huanhuan for summaries.

36:54.990 --> 36:56.230
You're in charge of recording it

36:56.230 --> 36:57.640
and giving it to me every day. Okay?

36:57.640 --> 36:58.190
Okay.

36:58.320 --> 36:59.230
Ms. Xu,

36:59.550 --> 37:00.900
why is that?

37:01.050 --> 37:02.270
Think about it.

37:02.400 --> 37:03.030
Every year,

37:03.030 --> 37:05.320
what days are June 7th to 10th?

37:07.110 --> 37:08.230
-The college entrance exam!
-The college entrance exam!

37:08.230 --> 37:10.280
But the graded exam
for the three elective subjects

37:10.280 --> 37:12.190
was already taken last week, wasn't it?

37:12.190 --> 37:13.400
So we just can't miss the exam

37:13.400 --> 37:14.660
for the three compulsory subjects.

37:14.660 --> 37:17.070
Since the bookings
have given us enough hints,

37:17.070 --> 37:18.870
we can't miss this opportunity.

37:19.190 --> 37:20.310
But

37:20.510 --> 37:22.040
what if it's a coincidence?

37:22.110 --> 37:24.400
Our Purong Hotel is a five-star hotel.

37:24.400 --> 37:25.550
Staying in our hotel for a day,

37:25.550 --> 37:28.280
with meals and accommodation,
would cost over 1,000 yuan, right?

37:28.280 --> 37:30.800
How many college entrance exam-takers'
families can afford that?

37:30.800 --> 37:31.880
Besides,

37:32.400 --> 37:34.760
who knows if there's an exam site nearby?

37:35.520 --> 37:36.920
Whether it's a coincidence
or an opportunity,

37:36.920 --> 37:39.040
we need to find out
before we discuss further.

37:39.040 --> 37:39.840
In our area,

37:39.840 --> 37:40.920
the "3+3" new pattern

37:40.920 --> 37:42.920
of the college entrance exam
has been implemented for years.

37:42.920 --> 37:44.510
As for the quantity and locations

37:44.510 --> 37:46.110
of the exam sites each year,

37:46.110 --> 37:47.560
we should investigate them clearly.

37:47.560 --> 37:49.280
Hotels belong to the service industry.

37:49.280 --> 37:50.110
We can't just wait

37:50.110 --> 37:51.880
for guests to initiatively come to us.

37:51.880 --> 37:53.400
We need to take the initiative to discover

37:53.400 --> 37:54.360
the guests' needs

37:54.360 --> 37:56.160
and provide them with the best service.

37:56.160 --> 37:58.670
Only in this way can we stand out

37:58.670 --> 38:00.200
in the fierce competition.

38:00.360 --> 38:01.070
Got it?

38:01.230 --> 38:02.000
Understood.

38:02.510 --> 38:03.510
Let's get to work.

38:15.930 --> 38:16.550
What are you looking at

38:16.550 --> 38:17.400
so seriously?

38:17.580 --> 38:20.240
The college entrance exam sites
near our hotel.

38:21.690 --> 38:22.760
Since when have you been so obedient

38:22.760 --> 38:24.220
to Ms. Xu's instructions?

38:25.190 --> 38:27.920
I'm not being obedient
to Ms. Xu's instructions.

38:27.920 --> 38:30.110
My cousin will take
the college entrance exam this year.

38:30.110 --> 38:31.070
I'm just curious,

38:31.070 --> 38:32.730
so I'm looking it up casually.

38:34.880 --> 38:35.790
In my opinion,

38:35.820 --> 38:37.640
when it comes to the tasks
of getting clients,

38:37.640 --> 38:39.760
there should be some news
coming from the marketing

38:39.760 --> 38:41.670
and sales departments first, right?

38:41.670 --> 38:43.400
You and I are so well-informed,

38:43.400 --> 38:44.760
but we still don't know anything about it.

38:44.760 --> 38:46.360
It must be totally baseless.

38:46.360 --> 38:47.320
Ms. Xu really

38:47.320 --> 38:49.450
knows how to make trouble for herself.

38:49.920 --> 38:51.500
She's not making trouble for you.

38:51.500 --> 38:53.030
Why are you talking so much?

38:54.120 --> 38:55.040
Hurry up and eat.

38:55.040 --> 38:57.240
We have to change shifts after the meal.

39:04.920 --> 39:05.800
Ms. Xu,

39:05.820 --> 39:06.670
instead of having a meal,

39:06.670 --> 39:08.110
what are you busy with here?

39:08.110 --> 39:09.710
I'm doing a little research.

39:10.180 --> 39:12.160
Why are you circling
so many spots in red ink?

39:12.160 --> 39:13.400
Are you going to buy a house?

39:13.400 --> 39:14.710
No.

39:14.710 --> 39:17.280
I'm just checking where these
college entrance exam sites are.

39:17.280 --> 39:18.480
I'd like to see if there are any of them

39:18.480 --> 39:19.400
near our hotel.

39:20.190 --> 39:21.520
Don't bother with this.

39:21.710 --> 39:22.840
No college entrance exam sites

39:22.840 --> 39:24.670
have ever been set up near our hotel.

39:24.670 --> 39:27.130
Those exam-takers rarely
stay in our hotel.

39:27.510 --> 39:28.770
I'll get going, Ma'am.

39:36.690 --> 39:37.240
[Fuxing High School
Affiliated to Fudan University] [2.5 km]

39:37.270 --> 39:38.410
[The Affiliated High School
of East China Normal University] [1.5 km]

39:38.440 --> 39:39.710
[Xinhua Finance and Economics School]

39:59.510 --> 40:00.760
You're at home, huh?

40:01.850 --> 40:04.110
Why didn't you turn on the lights at home?

40:04.590 --> 40:07.050
You also didn't reply
to my WeChat messages.

40:10.030 --> 40:11.830
Why aren't you saying anything?

40:13.740 --> 40:15.870
You didn't close that window, either.

40:16.230 --> 40:17.000
It's so damp inside.

40:17.000 --> 40:19.260
Why didn't you turn on the dehumidifier?

40:32.890 --> 40:34.360
What's wrong with me
buying a pair of boots?

40:34.360 --> 40:36.070
I have to
carry such a big belly every day,

40:36.070 --> 40:37.230
and it's so heavy.

40:39.880 --> 40:41.080
The doctor told me...

40:42.710 --> 40:44.370
to go to the hospital tomorrow

40:46.360 --> 40:48.290
for an enhanced abdominal CT scan.

40:50.800 --> 40:52.320
Can you go with me?

41:00.400 --> 41:01.510
What's wrong?
